OOC:My post always arrive out of order this is number 1.

::Koj::
Grabs the last of his gear and climbs on Inu-Yasha."Lets go?"

::Inu-Yasha::
Inu Looks at Koj "What do you want on your tombstone?"

::Koj::
Koj thinks "If you mean pizza cheese and energy bites and on my grave "Koj 
the Last Dragon Master of Dare."

::Both::
Take off Flying towards the Alliance base laughing .((Fast Forward))

::Inu-Yasha::
Inu-Yasha Stops a few clicks outside the Alliance defense grid. "Good luck 
Koj."

::Koj::
Koj gets off Inu "thanks old friend" Koj scans the area cuts on his cloak 
and races around the base planting the Holocubes in various places as his 
optics show the target points as Koj returns to the last vector he mounts 
the holoprojector.
